{"tid":1971874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登批鬥風氣嚴重，建制藍絲或成為最大贏家？","createTime":"2020-04-14T08:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T08:02:46.000Z","uid":51592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c5296a97cb670ff9a9fa8fc745ee3a39116dfff5","tid":1971874,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:00:52.000Z","msg":"小弟發現選舉期越近，批鬥風氣似乎越黎越嚴重，由手足到黃店甚至黨派無一倖免，<br />\n小弟深明由上年6月至今所經歷令大家情緒變得敏感，容易焦躁，<br />\n有見及此，小弟作左個連登手足的溝通技巧希望可以避免產生言語衝突，促進生產力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n情境一，持不同意見時(一)    <br />\n不要說:「你五毛/分化撚/私怨撚」<br />\n試著說:「嗯，這很有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n情境二，持不同意見時(二)    <br />\n不要說:「屌你都唔撚柒明」<br />\n試著說:「你見解獨到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n情境三，手足做錯事<br />\n不要說:「獅鳥佢啦屌」<br />\n試著說:「我覺得你有改善的空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n歡迎下面投稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「多一點關心，少一點問候娘親，連登會更美好！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樹大有枯枝是必然的，出面既批鬥post麻煩大家善用不推文回覆或冷處理，<br />\n回覆前停一停諗一諗，<br />\n要清算，等打贏呢個政權再清算，好嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n希望大家毋忘初心 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不篤灰 不割席 <br />\n矛頭一致對外</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我們別再犯五年前的錯，好嗎？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477040\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477040</a>"},{"pid":"1e38d835a9594b5ca999293a05f410d186ba0268","tid":1971874,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"[即時生效]以後邊個再鬥黃就原地做一set體能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1969685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1969685</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d5db38eaea9765f4293a8cc00e76cf8b0cd3a20b","tid":1971874,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"natural instinct"}]}